trans-unit.source: Indicates the progress of an operation.
trans-unit.target: Angir fremdriften for en operasjon.

trans-unit.source: A ProgressBar control consists of a window that is filled, by default from left to right, as an operation progresses.
trans-unit.target: En fremdriftsindikatorkontrollen består av et vindu som er fylt, som standard fra venstre mot høyre, mens en operasjon pågår.

trans-unit.source: The control has a range and a current position.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen har et område, og gjeldende posisjon.

trans-unit.source: ProgressBar overrides the metadata of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RangeBase.Maximum%2A> property and sets its default to 100.
trans-unit.target: ProgressBar overstyrer metadataene i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RangeBase.Maximum%2A>egenskapen og setter standard til 100.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RangeBase.Maximum%2A>

trans-unit.source: ProgressBar overrides the metadata of the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A> property and sets its default to `false`.
trans-unit.target: ProgressBar overstyrer metadataene i <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>egenskapen og setter standard til `false`.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Dependency Properties Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [avhengighet egenskaper oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Customizing the ProgressBar Control To apply the same property settings to multiple ProgressBar controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Tilpasse ProgressBar kontrollen til i gjelder samme egenskapsinnstillingene flere ProgressBar kontroller, bruk av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can modify the default <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> to give the control a unique appearance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan endre standard <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>Gi kontrollen unikt utseende.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: For more information about creating a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, see [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om hvordan du oppretter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, se [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: To see the parts and states that are specific to the ProgressBar, see [ProgressBar Styles and Templates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se delene og statusene som er spesifikke for ProgressBar, kan du se [ProgressBar stiler og maler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Dependency properties for this control might be set by the control’s default style.
trans-unit.target: Avhengighet egenskapene for denne kontrollen, kan angis ved kontrollens standardstilen.

trans-unit.source: If a property is set by a default style, the property might change from its default value when the control appears in the application.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en egenskap er satt av en standardstilen, kan endre egenskapen standardverdi når kontrollen vises i applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The default style is determined by which desktop theme is used when the application is running.
trans-unit.target: Standardstilen er avhengig av hvilken stasjonær tema brukes når programmet kjører.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Default WPF Themes](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [standard WPF oppsett](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Setting a visual property will only have an effect if that property is both present in ProgressBar control's default template and is set by using a .
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Angi en visual egenskap trenger bare en effekt hvis egenskapen er begge finnes i ProgressBar kontrollens standardmalen og angis ved hjelp av en.

trans-unit.source: You can find a list of visual properties in the "Changing the Visual Structure of a Control" section in [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](../Topic/Customizing%20the%20Appearance%20of%20an%20Existing%20Control%20by%20Creating%20a%20ControlTemplate.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner en liste over visual egenskaper i delen "Endring i Visual strukturen av et kontroll" [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](../Topic/Customizing%20the%20Appearance%20of%20an%20Existing%20Control%20by%20Creating%20a%20ControlTemplate.md).
